text: Ayruz Abmammadova (; born 3 August 1978) is an Azerbaijani former footballer who played as a midfielder. She has been a member of the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers
